name: Hand Hoop Hand - Don't get tied up

metadata.name: Hand Hoop Hand - Don't get tied up
metadata.description:
This Photography was created as part of my friend and Aerial Hoop artist Joana Dias for her Circus School final Project.

We have walked around London to capture some artistic photos to include in her Portfolio.

An older work of mine that I am very proud and that I Love.

Some People will not like the fact that none of the lines on this image are straight but that is the idea. Because when she is performing, she hangs and fly all over.
